00:41:52,313 --> 00:42:15,719
and helping residents stay engaged and stable in their community before issue become crisis and be able to introduce the resources available for them, like the senior center. We do a lot, send them a lot there. Overall, this project directly support low income and senior residents.

93
00:42:16,141 --> 00:42:42,213
removes cultural and language barriers, and strengthens the wellbeing of some Medford most vulnerable population. One thing I wanna share with you, when we have those people, we have something with the Haitian community, they don't like to talk about healthcare. So when they are with us, they feel comfortable.

