00:47:07,690 --> 00:47:35,011
A little hard to read on my phone, but so we did an additional 148 shopping trips. We started a shuttle to Target and Walmart because people were looking for a shuttle to Target and Walmart. I've been working with Laurel on the Transportation Committee for a year, a year and a half or so, so some of the things come through those discussions.

107
00:47:36,479 --> 00:47:54,620
